      "title": "Fish Tank",
      "pageid": 4404,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><dl><dd><i>For the Fish Tank Bundles, see <a href=\"/Bundles#Fish_Tank\" title=\"Bundles\">Bundles#Fish Tank</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>Fish Tanks</b> are <a href=\"/Furniture\" title=\"Furniture\">furniture</a> items. There are different sizes of fish tanks that can house different numbers of items.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Use\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Use</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Allowed_Contents\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Allowed Contents</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Types\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Types</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Animations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Animations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Secret\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Secret</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Use\">Use</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Use\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Certain items can be added to the fish tank to change its appearance by holding the item and right-clicking on the tank. To get a list of the items inside or to remove them, right-click on the tank with empty hands. The location and appearance of the decorations and any stationary animals placed inside is random and can be changed without removing items by picking up and re-placing the tank.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Allowed_Contents\">Allowed Contents</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Allowed Contents\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Fish tanks are allowed to have the following contents:\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Category\n</th>\n<th>Count\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Items\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Decorations\n</td>\n<td>Small/Modern: 1<br />Others: 1 of each type\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Anchor.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c0/Anchor.png/24px-Anchor.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/c0/Anchor.png/36px-Anchor.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/c0/Anchor.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Anchor\" title=\"Anchor\">Anchor</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Ancient Sword.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/76/Ancient_Sword.png/24px-Ancient_Sword.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/76/Ancient_Sword.png/36px-Ancient_Sword.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/76/Ancient_Sword.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Ancient_Sword\" title=\"Ancient Sword\">Ancient Sword</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Clay.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Clay.png/24px-Clay.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a2/Clay.png/36px-Clay.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a2/Clay.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Clay\" title=\"Clay\">Clay</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Coral.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b1/Coral.png/24px-Coral.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/b1/Coral.png/36px-Coral.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/b1/Coral.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coral\" title=\"Coral\">Coral</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Hardwood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/24px-Hardwood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Hardwood.png/36px-Hardwood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Hardwood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Joja Cola.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Joja_Cola.png/24px-Joja_Cola.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Joja_Cola.png/36px-Joja_Cola.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d5/Joja_Cola.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Joja_Cola\" title=\"Joja Cola\">Joja Cola</a></span> <img alt=\"Springobjects789.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/Springobjects789.png/24px-Springobjects789.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/04/Springobjects789.png/36px-Springobjects789.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/04/Springobjects789.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Secrets#Lucky_Purple_Shorts\" title=\"Secrets\">Lucky Purple Shorts</a> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Nautilus Shell.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a4/Nautilus_Shell.png/24px-Nautilus_Shell.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a4/Nautilus_Shell.png/36px-Nautilus_Shell.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a4/Nautilus_Shell.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Nautilus_Shell\" title=\"Nautilus Shell\">Nautilus Shell</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Pearl.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/73/Pearl.png/24px-Pearl.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/73/Pearl.png/36px-Pearl.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/73/Pearl.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearl</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Pineapple.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fb/Pineapple.png/24px-Pineapple.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/fb/Pineapple.png/36px-Pineapple.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/f/fb/Pineapple.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Pineapple\" title=\"Pineapple\">Pineapple</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Rainbow Shell.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3d/Rainbow_Shell.png/24px-Rainbow_Shell.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/3d/Rainbow_Shell.png/36px-Rainbow_Shell.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/3d/Rainbow_Shell.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Rainbow_Shell\" title=\"Rainbow Shell\">Rainbow Shell</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/13/Seaweed.png/24px-Seaweed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/13/Seaweed.png/36px-Seaweed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/13/Seaweed.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\">Seaweed</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Treasure Chest.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png/24px-Treasure_Chest.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png/36px-Treasure_Chest.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/32/Treasure_Chest.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Treasure_Chest\" title=\"Treasure Chest\">Treasure Chest</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bottom Creatures\n</td>\n<td>Limited amount, depending on type of fish tank\n</td>\n<td>Moving: <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Blobfish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7f/Blobfish.png/24px-Blobfish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/7f/Blobfish.png/36px-Blobfish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/7f/Blobfish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Blobfish\" title=\"Blobfish\">Blobfish</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Crab.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/63/Crab.png/24px-Crab.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/63/Crab.png/36px-Crab.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/63/Crab.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Crab\" title=\"Crab\">Crab</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Crayfish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/53/Crayfish.png/24px-Crayfish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/53/Crayfish.png/36px-Crayfish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/53/Crayfish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Crayfish\" title=\"Crayfish\">Crayfish</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Flounder.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/85/Flounder.png/24px-Flounder.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/85/Flounder.png/36px-Flounder.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/85/Flounder.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Flounder\" title=\"Flounder\">Flounder</a></span> <img alt=\"Green Frog Egg.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/23/Green_Frog_Egg.png/24px-Green_Frog_Egg.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/2/23/Green_Frog_Egg.png/36px-Green_Frog_Egg.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/2/23/Green_Frog_Egg.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Frog_Egg\" title=\"Frog Egg\">Frog</a> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Lobster.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9f/Lobster.png/24px-Lobster.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/9f/Lobster.png/36px-Lobster.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/9f/Lobster.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Lobster\" title=\"Lobster\">Lobster</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sandfish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/bb/Sandfish.png/24px-Sandfish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/b/bb/Sandfish.png/36px-Sandfish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/b/bb/Sandfish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Sandfish\" title=\"Sandfish\">Sandfish</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Snail.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/Snail.png/24px-Snail.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d2/Snail.png/36px-Snail.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d2/Snail.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Snail\" title=\"Snail\">Snail</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stonefish.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/03/Stonefish.png/24px-Stonefish.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/0/03/Stonefish.png/36px-Stonefish.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/0/03/Stonefish.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stonefish\" title=\"Stonefish\">Stonefish</a></span>\n</td>\n<td>Stationary: <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Clam.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Clam.png/24px-Clam.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/ed/Clam.png/36px-Clam.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/ed/Clam.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Clam\" title=\"Clam\">Clam</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Cockle.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ad/Cockle.png/24px-Cockle.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/ad/Cockle.png/36px-Cockle.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/ad/Cockle.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Cockle\" title=\"Cockle\">Cockle</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Mussel.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/aa/Mussel.png/24px-Mussel.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/aa/Mussel.png/36px-Mussel.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/aa/Mussel.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Mussel\" title=\"Mussel\">Mussel</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Periwinkle.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Periwinkle.png/24px-Periwinkle.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1d/Periwinkle.png/36px-Periwinkle.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/1d/Periwinkle.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Periwinkle\" title=\"Periwinkle\">Periwinkle</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Oyster.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/54/Oyster.png/24px-Oyster.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/54/Oyster.png/36px-Oyster.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/5/54/Oyster.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Oyster\" title=\"Oyster\">Oyster</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sea Cucumber.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Sea_Cucumber.png/24px-Sea_Cucumber.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a9/Sea_Cucumber.png/36px-Sea_Cucumber.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/a/a9/Sea_Cucumber.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Sea_Cucumber\" title=\"Sea Cucumber\">Sea Cucumber</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Sea Urchin.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Sea_Urchin.png/24px-Sea_Urchin.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e7/Sea_Urchin.png/36px-Sea_Urchin.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e7/Sea_Urchin.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Sea_Urchin\" title=\"Sea Urchin\">Sea Urchin</a></span> <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Super Cucumber.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Super_Cucumber.png/24px-Super_Cucumber.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d5/Super_Cucumber.png/36px-Super_Cucumber.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d5/Super_Cucumber.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Super_Cucumber\" title=\"Super Cucumber\">Super Cucumber</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Swimming Creatures\n</td>\n<td>Limited amount, depending on type of fish tank\n</td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Shrimp.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Shrimp.png/24px-Shrimp.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Shrimp.png/36px-Shrimp.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/91/Shrimp.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Shrimp\" title=\"Shrimp\">Shrimp</a></span> All other fish\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Types\">Types</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Types\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>There are 7 types of fish tanks. The <a href=\"/Small_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Small Fish Tank\">Small Fish Tank</a>, <a href=\"/Modern_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Modern Fish Tank\">Modern Fish Tank</a>, <a href=\"/Large_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Large Fish Tank\">Large Fish Tank</a>, and <a href=\"/Deluxe_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Deluxe Fish Tank\">Deluxe Fish Tank</a> are available from the <a href=\"/Furniture_Catalogue\" title=\"Furniture Catalogue\">Furniture Catalogue</a> and the Deluxe Fish Tank is available in Willy's shop only after completing the <a href=\"/Quests#Tropical_Fish\" title=\"Quests\">Tropical Fish</a> special order. The <a href=\"/Jungle_Tank\" title=\"Jungle Tank\">Jungle Tank</a> is only available from the <a href=\"/Giant_Stump\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Raccoon</a> after its 5th request. The <a href=\"/Bundles#Fish_Tank\" title=\"Bundles\">Community Center Fish Tank</a> is only available after the Fish Tank bundles are completed (which turns the broken fish tank into a working fish tank) and cannot be obtained in any other way, nor can it be picked up to change the location or appearance of static decor placed in it. The <a href=\"/Aquatic_Sanctuary\" title=\"Aquatic Sanctuary\">Aquatic Sanctuary</a> is only available from <a href=\"/Qi%27s_Walnut_Room\" title=\"Qi&#39;s Walnut Room\">Qi's Walnut Room</a> and cannot be found in the Furniture Catalogue.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Item\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Shop\" title=\"Fish Shop\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/73/Willy_Icon.png/24px-Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png 1.5x\" /></a> Price\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/Furniture_Catalogue\" title=\"Furniture Catalogue\"><img alt=\"Furniture Catalogue.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e8/Furniture_Catalogue.png/24px-Furniture_Catalogue.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e8/Furniture_Catalogue.png/36px-Furniture_Catalogue.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e8/Furniture_Catalogue.png/48px-Furniture_Catalogue.png 2x\" /></a> Price\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/Qi%27s_Walnut_Room\" title=\"Qi&#39;s Walnut Room\"><img alt=\"Mr. Qi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/4f/Mr._Qi_Icon.png/24px-Mr._Qi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/4/4f/Mr._Qi_Icon.png 1.5x\" /></a> Price\n</th>\n<th>Allowed amount of bottom creatures\n</th>\n<th>Allowed amount of swimming creatures\n</th>\n<th>Furniture size\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Small Fish Tank.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/79/Small_Fish_Tank.png/32px-Small_Fish_Tank.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/79/Small_Fish_Tank.png/48px-Small_Fish_Tank.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/7/79/Small_Fish_Tank.png/64px-Small_Fish_Tank.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Small_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Small Fish Tank\">Small Fish Tank</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0500\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />500g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"0\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />0g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Modern Fish Tank.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1a/Modern_Fish_Tank.png/32px-Modern_Fish_Tank.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1a/Modern_Fish_Tank.png/48px-Modern_Fish_Tank.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/1a/Modern_Fish_Tank.png/64px-Modern_Fish_Tank.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Modern_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Modern Fish Tank\">Modern Fish Tank</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"0\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />0g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Fish Tank.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Large_Fish_Tank.png/64px-Large_Fish_Tank.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/94/Large_Fish_Tank.png/96px-Large_Fish_Tank.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/94/Large_Fish_Tank.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Large Fish Tank\">Large Fish Tank</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"2000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"2000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />2,000g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"0\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />0g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Jungle Tank.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/84/Jungle_Tank.png/64px-Jungle_Tank.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/84/Jungle_Tank.png/96px-Jungle_Tank.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/84/Jungle_Tank.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Jungle_Tank\" title=\"Jungle Tank\">Jungle Tank</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>4\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Deluxe Fish Tank.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Deluxe_Fish_Tank.png/80px-Deluxe_Fish_Tank.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"80\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/46/Deluxe_Fish_Tank.png/120px-Deluxe_Fish_Tank.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/46/Deluxe_Fish_Tank.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Deluxe_Fish_Tank\" title=\"Deluxe Fish Tank\">Deluxe Fish Tank</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"5000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"5000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />5,000g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"0\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />0g</span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img alt=\"Community Center Fish Tank icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png/80px-Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"80\" height=\"60\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png/120px-Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/3/37/Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png/160px-Community_Center_Fish_Tank_icon.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Bundles#Fish_Tank\" title=\"Bundles\">Community Center Fish Tank</a></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Aquatic Sanctuary.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/14/Aquatic_Sanctuary.png/112px-Aquatic_Sanctuary.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"112\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/14/Aquatic_Sanctuary.png/168px-Aquatic_Sanctuary.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/1/14/Aquatic_Sanctuary.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Aquatic_Sanctuary\" title=\"Aquatic Sanctuary\">Aquatic Sanctuary</a></span></td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0000\">N/A</td>\n<td data-sort-value=\"0020\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"20\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Qi Gem.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/78/Qi_Gem.png/24px-Qi_Gem.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/7/78/Qi_Gem.png/36px-Qi_Gem.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/7/78/Qi_Gem.png 2x\" /> 20</span></td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>7\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Animations\">Animations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Animations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Most of the swimming creatures either move around without animating (<i>e.g.,</i> <a href=\"/Pufferfish\" title=\"Pufferfish\">Pufferfish</a>, <a href=\"/Octopus\" title=\"Octopus\">Octopus</a>) or move their tails / rear parts of their bodies at various speeds while swimming. However, some of the swimming creatures have unique animations:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Eel\" title=\"Eel\">Eels</a> and <a href=\"/Lava_Eel\" title=\"Lava Eel\">Lava Eels</a> undulate up and down like a dolphin or whale (rather than side to side like an eel or other fish).</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Squid\" title=\"Squid\">Squids</a> and <a href=\"/Midnight_Squid\" title=\"Midnight Squid\">Midnight Squids</a> push with their tentacles much like the <a href=\"/Blue_Squid\" title=\"Blue Squid\">Blue Squid</a> found in the mines with the <a href=\"/The_Mines#Shrine_of_Challenge\" title=\"The Mines\">Shrine of Challenge</a> active.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Stingray\" title=\"Stingray\">Stingrays</a> flip their fins up and down as well as moving their tails.</li></ul>\n<p>For the bottom creatures, <a href=\"/Frog_Egg\" title=\"Frog Egg\">Frogs</a> have unique animations for hopping around and inflating their vocal sacs.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Secret\">Secret</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Secret\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" style=\"\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><b>Details</b>&#160;\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>It's possible to place a <a href=\"/Hats\" title=\"Hats\">hat</a> on a <a href=\"/Sea_Urchin\" title=\"Sea Urchin\">Sea Urchin</a> in any fish tank by selecting the hat and right-clicking on the tank.\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Fish_Tank&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Can now add <a href=\"/Anchor\" title=\"Anchor\">Anchors</a>, <a href=\"/Treasure_Chest\" title=\"Treasure Chest\">Treasure Chests</a>, <a href=\"/Pearl\" title=\"Pearl\">Pearls</a>, and <a href=\"/Frog_Egg\" title=\"Frog Egg\">Frog Eggs</a> to Fish Tanks. Added <a href=\"/Jungle_Tank\" title=\"Jungle Tank\">Jungle Tank</a> and <a href=\"/Bundles#Fish_Tank\" title=\"Bundles\">Community Center Fish Tank</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.4</a>: Can now add <a href=\"/Pineapple\" title=\"Pineapple\">Pineapples</a>, <a href=\"/Ancient_Sword\" title=\"Ancient Sword\">Ancient Swords</a>, <a href=\"/Hardwood\" title=\"Hardwood\">Hardwood</a>, <a href=\"/Nautilus_Shell\" title=\"Nautilus Shell\">Nautilus Shells</a>, <a href=\"/Rainbow_Shell\" title=\"Rainbow Shell\">Rainbow Shells</a>, <a href=\"/Joja_Cola\" title=\"Joja Cola\">Joja Cola</a>, <a href=\"/Secrets#Lucky_Purple_Shorts\" title=\"Secrets\">Lucky Purple Shorts</a>, and <a href=\"/Clay\" title=\"Clay\">Clay</a> to Fish Tanks.</li></ul>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414025652\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.112 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.120 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 6533/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8021/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1641/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 13536/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   53.621      1 -total\n 79.71%   42.742     36 Template:Name\n  8.12%    4.355      8 Template:Price\n  4.80%    2.572      3 Template:History\n  2.77%    1.483      3 Template:Version\n  2.24%    1.199      1 Template:Collapse\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:4404-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414025652 and revision id 190200\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": ":''For the Fish Tank Bundles, see [[Bundles#Fish Tank]].''\n\n'''Fish Tanks''' are [[furniture]] items. There are different sizes of fish tanks that can house different numbers of items.\n\n==Use==\nCertain items can be added to the fish tank to change its appearance by holding the item and right-clicking on the tank. To get a list of the items inside or to remove them, right-click on the tank with empty hands. The location and appearance of the decorations and any stationary animals placed inside is random and can be changed without removing items by picking up and re-placing the tank.\n\n==Allowed Contents==\nFish tanks are allowed to have the following contents:\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Category\n! Count\n! colspan=\"2\"|Items\n|-\n| Decorations\n| Small/Modern: 1<br />Others: 1 of each type\n| colspan=\"2\"|{{Name|Anchor}} {{Name|Ancient Sword}} {{Name|Clay}} {{Name|Coral}} {{Name|Hardwood}} {{Name|Joja Cola}} [[File:Springobjects789.png|24px|link=]] [[Secrets#Lucky Purple Shorts|Lucky Purple Shorts]] {{Name|Nautilus Shell}} {{Name|Pearl}} {{Name|Pineapple}} {{Name|Rainbow Shell}} {{Name|Seaweed}} {{Name|Stone}} {{Name|Treasure Chest}} \n|-\n| Bottom Creatures\n| Limited amount, depending on type of fish tank\n| Moving: {{Name|Blobfish}} {{Name|Crab}} {{Name|Crayfish}} {{Name|Flounder}} [[File:Green Frog Egg.png|24px|link=]] [[Frog Egg|Frog]] {{Name|Lobster}} {{Name|Sandfish}} {{Name|Snail}} {{Name|Stonefish}}\n| Stationary: {{Name|Clam}} {{Name|Cockle}} {{Name|Mussel}} {{Name|Periwinkle}} {{Name|Oyster}} {{Name|Sea Cucumber}} {{Name|Sea Urchin}} {{Name|Super Cucumber}}\n|-\n| Swimming Creatures\n| Limited amount, depending on type of fish tank\n| colspan=\"2\"|{{Name|Shrimp}} All other fish\n|}\n\n==Types==\nThere are 7 types of fish tanks. The [[Small Fish Tank]], [[Modern Fish Tank]], [[Large Fish Tank]], and [[Deluxe Fish Tank]] are available from the [[Furniture Catalogue]] and the Deluxe Fish Tank is available in Willy's shop only after completing the [[Quests#Tropical Fish|Tropical Fish]] special order. The [[Jungle Tank]] is only available from the [[Giant Stump|Raccoon]] after its 5th request. The [[Bundles#Fish Tank|Community Center Fish Tank]] is only available after the Fish Tank bundles are completed (which turns the broken fish tank into a working fish tank) and cannot be obtained in any other way, nor can it be picked up to change the location or appearance of static decor placed in it. The [[Aquatic Sanctuary]] is only available from [[Qi's Walnut Room]] and cannot be found in the Furniture Catalogue.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Item\n![[File:Willy Icon.png|24px|link=Fish Shop]] Price\n![[File:Furniture Catalogue.png|24px|link=Furniture Catalogue]] Price\n![[File:Mr. Qi Icon.png|24px|link=Qi's Walnut Room]] Price\n!Allowed amount of bottom creatures\n!Allowed amount of swimming creatures\n!Furniture size\n|-\n|{{Name|Small Fish Tank|size=32}} ||data-sort-value=\"0500\"|{{Price|500}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|{{Price|0}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 1 || 1 || 2\n|-\n|{{Name|Modern Fish Tank|size=32}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|{{Price|0}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 1 || 1 || 2\n|-\n|{{Name|Large Fish Tank|size=64}} ||data-sort-value=\"2000\"|{{Price|2000}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|{{Price|0}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 3 || 3 || 4\n|-\n|{{Name|Jungle Tank|size=64}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 4 || 3 || 4\n|-\n|{{Name|Deluxe Fish Tank|size=80}} ||data-sort-value=\"5000\"|{{Price|5000}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|{{Price|0}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 4 || 4 || 5\n|-\n|[[File:Community Center Fish Tank icon.png|80px|link=]] [[Bundles#Fish Tank|Community Center Fish Tank]] ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A || 5 || 5 || 6\n|-\n|{{Name|Aquatic Sanctuary|size=112}} ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0000\"|N/A ||data-sort-value=\"0020\"|{{Price|20|gem}} || 6 || 6 || 7\n|- \n|}\n\n==Animations==\nMost of the swimming creatures either move around without animating (''e.g.,'' [[Pufferfish]], [[Octopus]]) or move their tails / rear parts of their bodies at various speeds while swimming. However, some of the swimming creatures have unique animations:\n*[[Eel]]s and [[Lava Eel]]s undulate up and down like a dolphin or whale (rather than side to side like an eel or other fish).\n*[[Squid]]s and [[Midnight Squid]]s push with their tentacles much like the [[Blue Squid]] found in the mines with the [[The Mines#Shrine of Challenge|Shrine of Challenge]] active.\n*[[Stingray]]s flip their fins up and down as well as moving their tails.\nFor the bottom creatures, [[Frog Egg|Frogs]] have unique animations for hopping around and inflating their vocal sacs.\n\n==Secret==\n{{collapse|content=\nIt's possible to place a [[Hats|hat]] on a [[Sea Urchin]] in any fish tank by selecting the hat and right-clicking on the tank.}}\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.5|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.6|Can now add [[Anchor]]s, [[Treasure Chest]]s, [[Pearl]]s, and [[Frog Egg]]s to Fish Tanks. Added [[Jungle Tank]] and [[Bundles#Fish Tank|Community Center Fish Tank]].}}\n{{History|1.6.4|Can now add [[Pineapple]]s, [[Ancient Sword]]s, [[Hardwood]], [[Nautilus Shell]]s, [[Rainbow Shell]]s, [[Joja Cola]], [[Secrets#Lucky Purple Shorts|Lucky Purple Shorts]], and [[Clay]] to Fish Tanks.}}\n\n[[Category:Fish Tanks]]\n\n[[de:Aquarium]]\n[[es:Pecera]]\n[[fr:Aquarium]]\n[[it:Acquario]]\n[[ja:水槽]]\n[[ko:수조]]\n[[hu:Haltartály]]\n[[pt:Aquário]]\n[[ru:Аквариум]]\n[[tr:Akvaryum]]\n[[zh:鱼缸]]"
    }
  }
}